title: One Piece Color [JK]
author: Eiichiro Oda
description: Digitally colored comics exist in Japanese. Official English translations convey the story most accurately, but also have some issues with translating names that I’m not a fan of. They also only exist in black and white. I am simply taking One Piece and One Piece and combining them to create… One Piece! Some examples of translation deviations: “Zolo” => “Zoro”, “Navy” => “Marines”, etc.
